transcript.text: Welcome to on print shop.
Today we will see how to create corporate auto profiling.
To create a auto profiling for a corporate, first of all you will need to add PDF block templates for that particular corporate.
Remember you need to add PDF block templates because corporate auto profiling only works on PDF block templates.
So the way I have added over here the PDF block template for a particular corporate, in the same way you will need to add the PDF block templates for that particular corporate.
While adding the PDF block template, you keep in mind to activate this centralized personalization as well as personalization profiles.
And then you can click on 7 continue and add a PDF block template.

After adding the PDF block templates over here, you just need to go to admin, go to a particular corporate, click on action button and click on corporate profile Over here in the corporate profile, you'll need to add corporate profile form fields.
Remember one thing that corporate profile form fields should be same as the PDF block template fields name.
Over here the block name should be same as the corporate profile form fields.
So just click on add button to add a corporate profile form field.
Add the title over here like say name.
So it should be name then you can add the description over here then the block name.
So the block name should be exact the same as it is in the PDF block.
The same name of the block should be there.
So here the block name is name.
So I'll need the add the name block as name then available to corporate or a specific department that you select from here.
If for specific department then you can select departments from here otherwise keep it on corporates.
Then if you have added the field group then you can select the field group from here.
Add the sort order status then type like it will be a text box, radio button, drop down text area, upload file button or a late picker and then you can select over here personalize only.
The personalization fields will be editable to admin only.
If you select personalization only, then if you want to make it mandatory then you can select required or numeric or required and numeric or read only format or you can keep allow null if you want.
Don't go to make the field mandatory then you add the default value over here.
If you want to add any default value for this specific block or form field and then click on save and back and the profile form field will be added over here.

You can also add profile form fields in bulk by clicking on this import profile button over here in top right hand corner or over here you can download the file, select the department, download the file.
If you want any help go to Step 2, upload the file from here, map database form field in next step and then import data summary when you click on import button.
So this is how you can also import the profile.
Also you can personalize the profiles, import the personalized profiles from here.
You can add import personalized profile from import personalized profiles button, or you can click on simply a add button and add a personalized profile over here.
OK, after adding all these over here as a customer or as an employee, when an employee goes to the storefront and logs in from here, he'll need to go to my accounts.
Then he'll need to go to corporate profile over here.
After going to the corporate profile, he'll need to add his corporate profile details over here.

Let's say title, name, date of birth, then it's his personalized information, e-mail ID, fax, phone, blood, group, employee number, his profile picture over here, then the department credentials and designation, and then click on submit and continue.
So once the employee clicks on submit button, the corporate profile is submitted and saved in his particular account.

After adding the corporate profile, when customer once again logs in to his account, he'll just need to click on the particular PDF block template to customize and his details will be auto fetched over here.
Like over here.
You can see the details are auto fetched from his corporate profile in the same way it can be for the different different products also like say over here here in the ID card you can see over here.
The details will be auto fetched over here.
You can see over here.
So likewise it can also be done for the envelopes and literates also.
And after the details are auto fetched, you'll just need to click on the continue button and rest of the ordering process is same.
So this is how you can create auto profiling for a particular corporate.
Thank you for watching this video.

ocr.text: How to create Corporate Auto Profiling ?
Edit Info » Business Cards - Demo Bank
Tick to centralize the left-panel for all the block template pages. The PDF block name must be same for all the blocks in which you want to be able to use this option. Suppose "John Doe" is
the text entered in "Name" block of first page, the text in "Name" block will be replaced with "John Doe" in all the "Name" blocks in different pages of the concerned block template.
Tick if you want to enable the personalization Profile blocks to be auto filled for the corporate users from the left panel in the HTML studio.
Block name should be email,phone,firstname, lastname,street,postcode,state,country,companyname etc.
The personalization Profile will be available only for corporate users. not for retail users.
Edit Info > Business Cards - Demo Bank
Fix Billing Address Fix Shipping Address
Home > Corporates > Corporate Profile Form Fields
It is form fields which can be used to design corporate profile form, this form can be fill up by customer at login time.
Every element form is associated with the specific block of templates, and at studio page, filled data will be auto populated on associated block data.
File Edit View Plug-Ins Window Help PDFlib Blocks
Add Corporate Profile Form Field » DemoBank
A Home > Corporates > Corporate Profile > Add Corporate Profile Form Field
Name of block which will be linked to this form field.
The option selected above would be displayed as form control in form.
Home > Corporates > Corporate Profile > Import Profile
Corporate profile import will be allowed only through Excel.
First row in excel(excel heading) MUST be require.
Do not delete/modify any header titles.
Corproate Profile option like radio,dropdown values are available in second sheet.
Records which are highlighted in red color are mandatory.
Enter ID as per shown in Corporates/Departments tab
Upload only CSV File, only correct information will be uploaded from file.
Upload zip file containing images that you want to use in fields .All image files
should be placed directly in zip files, i.e. image file should not be in any folder.
C Admin :: Corporate Profile Fo X
It is form fields which can be used to design corporate profile forrhSthis form can be fill up by customer at login time.
Home > Corporates > Corporate Profile > Personalization Profiles
Bellow are the form fields which can be used to define a personalization profile, the personalization profile can only be edited by admin user only.
The personalization profile fields can be associated with PDF Block Templates biocks which will be user in template personalization for the user.
